                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Wangshu Inn has means of \"turning down\" the request of less-than-courteous guests to stay. One can practically deduce the scene when said rude guests are expelled from the blithe smile on Verr Goldet's face...",
